===Etymology 1===
From {{etyl|enm|en}} {{m|enm|twig}}, {{m|enm|twyg}}, from {{etyl|ang|en}} {{term|twīg|lang=ang}}, from {{etyl|gem-pro|en}} {{m|gem-pro|*twīgą}} (compare West Frisian {{term|twiich|lang=fy}}, {{etyl|nl|-}} {{term|twijg|lang=nl}}, {{etyl|de|-}} {{term|Zweig|lang=de}}), from {{etyl|ine-pro|en}} {{m|ine-pro|*dwigʰa}} (compare {{etyl|cu|-}} {{m|cu|двигъ||branch}}, {{etyl|sq|-}} {{m|sq|degë||branch}}), from {{m|ine-pro|*dwóh₁}}. More at [[two]].

